description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to former NFL lineman Ross Tucker about which 2-0 he thinks will not make the playoffs in the NFL. McLovin calls in from the set of Adam Sandler's movie set to practice his lines for Dan. Albert Breer discusses what Kyler Murray is doing right. And Carson Palmer says who he'd look at for the next USC Head Coach
